Class ResourceLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.vis.visuals.ResourceLoader

  • public class ResourceLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Tess Daughton 11/14/15. This class will be used to load and contain resources necessary for the Visualization rendering. images DIFF_FORESTFIRE - http://nobacks.com/photos/nature/page/39/ DIFF_CLOUD - http://nobacks.com/photos/nature/page/39/ DIFF_BLIGHT - http://www.clipartbest.com/cliparts/bcy/4Gj/bcy4GjgcL.jpeg
